:::
:::


甚至还可以用图像作为标题:


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data |>
  gt() |>
  tab_header(
    title = md("**A table with an image as title**"),
    subtitle = html(
      "<div style='text-align:center;'><img src='./image/Rlogo.png' height='60'></div>"
    )
  )
```

