#### 跨列标题

`tab_spanner()` 函数可以创建跨列的标题(合并单元格):


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data |>
  gt() |>
   tab_spanner(
    label = "Number",
    columns = c(GDP, Population)) |>
  tab_spanner(
    label = "Label",
    columns = c(Country, Capitals)
  )
```

