#### 多模型合并


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data(trial)

model_reglog <- glm(response ~ trt + grade, data = trial, family = binomial) |>
  tbl_regression()

model_cox  <- coxph(Surv(ttdeath, death) ~ trt + grade, data = trial) |>
  tbl_regression()

tbl_merge(
  list(model_reglog, model_cox),
  tab_spanner = c("**Tumor Response**", "**Time to Death**")
)
```

